Package aom.scripting.xs.tr

Class Unit

Object
Unit
public class Unit
extends Object
This class provides a collection of Trigger commands concerning Units.
Author:
Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com

      public int trUnitGetHeading​(string scenarioName)
      Returns the units heading. The angle returned is the angle the unit's face makes with the z-axis of the map. Unfortunately it does not say which side, so the result is always in the [0-180] interval.
